SO-O-O-O
YOU WOULD LIKE TO DELVE INTO THE ART
OF HARASSING,PESTERING,ANNOYING &
POSSIBLY HARMING ANOTHER ENEMY!!!

OK-HERE YOU'LL LEARN SOME OF THE USE-
FUL METHODS IV'E USED! FOR THE
SQUIMESH & CRYBABIES,DO NOT CONTINUE
READING THIS ARTICLE!

ITEM 1-

TO TORMENT A PERSON,ALLWAYS START OFF
EASY & SLOWLY INCREASE THE SEVERITY
OF YOUR ATTACK UNTIL YOUR GOAL IS
ACCOMPLISHED!HERE ILL GIVE YOU AN EX-
AMPLE OF JUST SUCH AN ATTACK! TRY TO
KEEP YOUR ENEMY UNNERVED THROUGHOUT
THE ATTACK BY SENDING ANONYMOUSE 
LETTERS & CALLS TO THEM, THROUGHOUT
THE DURATION OF YOUR ATTACK LETTING
THEM KNOW THAT YOUR NOT DONE WITH 
THEM YET!

ITEM 2-

TO START YOUR REVENGE,MAIL ANONYMOUSE
LETTERS & CALL AT ALL HOURS!

ITEM 3-

CALL THE PAPERS-PLACE ADS IN THEIR
NAME (1964 CHEVY IMPALLA-$600)WILL
GET EVERY MEXICAN GANG MEMBER IN L.A.
TO CALL & VISIT THEIR ADDRESS IF YOU 
PUT IT IN THE PAPER.

ITEM 4-
 ADVERTISE SOMETHING ILLEGAL IN THEIR
NAME,THEN CALL THE COPS & SHOW THEM
THE AD,OR JUST ANONYMOUSLY CLIP THE
AD & SEND IT TO THE COPS!
 CALL LONG DISTANCE UNDER THEIR PHONE
# AND ORDER CANDY & FLOWERS FROM 
WESTERN UNION UNDER THEIR #. ORDER
MAGAZINE SUBSCCRIPTIONS,BOOKS RECORDS
,EVERYTHING
YOU CAN,& HAVE IT SENT TO THEIR NAME
& ADDRESS!  PREFERABLY IF YOU KNOW 
WHERE THEY WORK-DUPLICATE YOUR 
EFFORTS & DO ALL THE ABOVE USING 
THEIR NAME.AND ALSO THEIR PLACE OF
EMPLOYMENT.


